# ==========================================
# Terraform Ignore Patterns
# ==========================================

# Local .terraform path containing plugin binaries
**/terraform/.terraform/

# Terraform state files (contain passwords and resource secrets)
**/terraform/*.tfstate
**/terraform/*.tfstate.backup
**/terraform/*.tfstate.lock.info

# Terraform variable definitions (might contain sensitive credentials)
**/terraform/*.tfvars
**/terraform/*.tfvars.json

# Ignore override files
**/terraform/override.tf
**/terraform/override.tf.json
**/terraform/*_override.tf
**/terraform/*_override.tf.json

# CLI configuration files
**/terraform/.terraformrc
**/terraform/terraform.rc

# Ignore dynamically-generated private SSH keys
**/*.pem

# ==========================================
# Ansible Ignore Patterns
# ==========================================

# Ansible retry files (generated upon task failures)
**/*.retry

# Ansible execution logs
**/ansible/*.log

# Local secrets or password files
**/ansible/.vault_pass
**/ansible/*_vault
**/ansible/*.vault
